[I] Python bindings for GStreamer

[T] GStreamer Python Bindings provide Python bindings for the GStreamer
[T] project. These bindings provide access to almost all of the GStreamer
[T] C API through an object oriented Python API.

[U] https://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/

